WEBVTT

00:00.008 --> 00:03.382
<i>- Previously on...
- Blood Drive!</i>

00:03.430 --> 00:04.984
<i>The fuck did you do to my car?</i>

00:05.023 --> 00:06.156
Who the hell are you?

00:06.190 --> 00:08.325
Allow me to introduce myself.

00:08.359 --> 00:10.761
Julian Slink, professional killer.

00:10.795 --> 00:12.329
<i>He knows where my sister is.</i>

00:12.363 --> 00:15.198
The question is, are you
gonna help me get it out of him?

00:15.233 --> 00:16.265
<i>[Dramatic Music]</i>

00:16.300 --> 00:17.501
[Photo Snaps]

00:17.535 --> 00:19.336
I'm in the belly of the beast, man.

00:19.370 --> 00:21.038
You were right. You fucking called it.

00:21.072 --> 00:22.372
They got their hands in everything.

00:22.407 --> 00:24.207
Politics, pharmaceuticals,
medical supplies.

00:24.242 --> 00:25.342
Remember Officer Aki?

00:25.376 --> 00:28.378
Heart can heal that eye of yours.

00:28.413 --> 00:30.080
Think she's kind of into me.

00:30.114 --> 00:33.016
Catch that Heart logo
back in Steel City?

00:33.051 --> 00:34.351
<i>Heart's behind Trioxin.</i>

00:34.385 --> 00:36.019
If they have the technology,

00:36.054 --> 00:37.454
how the hell can anyone stop them?

00:37.488 --> 00:39.122
[Wails]

00:39.157 --> 00:41.325
[Blows Thudding, Crunching]

00:43.561 --> 00:45.529
We're ready for you now.

00:45.563 --> 00:47.564
Oh.

00:47.613 --> 00:50.782
<i>[Brooding Tone]</i>

00:53.805 --> 00:56.340
<i>Heart Entertainment Presents
"The Slinks,"</i>

00:56.374 --> 00:59.076
<i>filmed in front of
a live studio audience.</i>

00:59.110 --> 01:00.410
I'm home.

01:00.445 --> 01:03.413
[Cheers And Applause]

01:03.448 --> 01:05.282
<i>♪</i>

01:05.316 --> 01:07.117
[Both Exhale, Sniff]

01:07.151 --> 01:08.485
[Crowd Awws]

01:08.519 --> 01:10.253
Ooh, what a day.

01:10.288 --> 01:11.388
[Chuckles]

01:11.422 --> 01:13.423
[Soft Groan]

01:13.458 --> 01:16.226
Julian, you have a minute?

01:16.260 --> 01:17.594
For you, sweetie, I've got ten.

01:17.628 --> 01:19.396
[Laughter]

01:19.430 --> 01:21.131
Well, it's about Melvin.

01:21.165 --> 01:24.182
He's been hiding something
under his bed.

01:25.603 --> 01:26.570
<i>[Comic Whistle]</i>

01:26.604 --> 01:27.795
Condoms.

01:27.920 --> 01:30.210
- [Crowd Gasps]
- What's our boy doing with condoms?

01:30.641 --> 01:32.476
Well, he's probably
not making balloon animals.

01:32.510 --> 01:34.611
[Laughter]

01:34.645 --> 01:36.113
[Laughing] I don't know.

01:36.147 --> 01:38.248
This is serious.

01:38.282 --> 01:39.483
You're right.

01:39.517 --> 01:41.485
Melvin!

01:41.519 --> 01:43.487
Get your keister in here.

01:43.521 --> 01:45.188
[Laughter, Applause]

01:45.223 --> 01:46.189
What'd I do now?

01:46.224 --> 01:48.158
More like who'd you do.

01:48.192 --> 01:49.359
[Laughter]

01:49.394 --> 01:52.129
You guys are going through my stuff?

01:52.864 --> 01:54.531
You should be happy.

01:54.565 --> 01:57.167
Some of my friends don't even use those.

01:57.201 --> 01:58.435
Ah, to be young.

01:58.469 --> 02:00.337
- [Pounding On Door]
- Who's that?

02:00.371 --> 02:02.139
You know, don't you worry, sweetie,

02:02.173 --> 02:03.607
if he catches something,
we'll take him to the doctor,

02:03.641 --> 02:06.176
give him a shot in the rump,
he'll be right as rain.

02:06.210 --> 02:08.544
- [Laughter]
- [Pounding Continues]

02:08.579 --> 02:10.614
[Growling And Groaning]

02:10.648 --> 02:11.848
Oh, my God!

02:11.883 --> 02:13.350
What's happening?

02:13.384 --> 02:15.585
<i>♪</i>

02:15.620 --> 02:18.422
<i>[dramatic musical stin</i>

02:18.456 --> 02:20.490
Help us, please!

02:20.525 --> 02:23.126
Ah, I love these little family chats.

02:23.161 --> 02:25.162
Oh, my God... [Screams]

02:25.196 --> 02:27.497
[Screaming Indistinctly]

02:27.532 --> 02:30.133
[Screaming] Oh, my God, Julian!

02:30.168 --> 02:31.835
[Growling And Groaning]

02:31.869 --> 02:33.837
No! No! No!

02:33.871 --> 02:36.640
[Screaming]

02:36.674 --> 02:39.643
[Both Screaming]

02:39.677 --> 02:41.134
And now,

02:41.312 --> 02:43.235
a word from our sponsor.

02:43.314 --> 02:46.283
<i>[Rock Music]</i>

02:46.317 --> 02:49.241
<i>♪</i>

