12:49.291 --> 12:51.292
"It's... it's getting hot in here."

12:51.326 --> 12:53.160
And that muffin
turns to the other muffin,

12:53.195 --> 12:54.295
says, "Oh, my...

12:54.329 --> 12:55.930
oh, my God, a talking muffin."

12:55.964 --> 12:59.333
[Crowd Booing]

12:59.368 --> 13:01.502
Kill the Cop! Kill the Cop!

13:01.536 --> 13:03.170
The only thing we're killing tonight

13:03.205 --> 13:04.505
is jokes, am I right?

13:04.539 --> 13:05.506
Kill the Cop! Kill the Cop!

13:05.540 --> 13:07.441
Oh...

13:07.476 --> 13:09.277
[Muffled Chanting Continues]
Kill the Cop! Kill the Cop!

13:09.311 --> 13:11.512
Crowd's all you care about.

13:11.546 --> 13:14.949
